18 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
19 SECTION 1. AMENDATORY Section 1, Chapter 7, 1st
20 Extraordinary Session, O.S.L. 2023 (73 O.S. Supp. 2024, Section
21 187A-5), is amended to read as follows:
22 Section 187A-5. A. In addition to any other authorization
23 provided by law, the Oklahoma Capitol Improvement Authority is
24 authorized to utilize available funds from the Legacy Capital
